<plot>High society, high times, and no end in sight. Shameless is an emotionally charged story about heroin, high living and the dramatic power of love as the last chance for survival. In the tradition of Leaving Las Vegas, Antonia (Elizabeth Hurley) begins a slow descent into the self-destructive world of heroin addiction, when she meets Mike, (C. Thomas Howell) in a chance encounter. At first she merely uses Mike to run errands to get the drugs she desperately needs. But after a night of passion, Antonia begins to fall in love and Mike knows he must use all of his resources to help Antonia overcome her habit soon or... it may kill her.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?350453</url></doc>
